{"TopicId":159670,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Challenge: Safely re-enter then land, or ditch, a vessel with 1 stock item and an external command seat (with a kerbal riding it).","CreatedByName":"Swingtyre","CreatedById":177111,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T18:14:43Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Swingtyre","CreatedById":177111,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T18:14:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EChallenge:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E Safely re-enter then land a vessel with 1 stock part and an external command seat (with a kerbal riding it). If either the part or command seat are destroyed, the attempt is a failure.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Numerlor","CreatedById":174198,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-23T21:13:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you tested this? I know it can be done with servicebay but you need to be really lucky. Nothing else comes into my mind without chutes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wibou7","CreatedById":155221,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-24T16:23:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223031932\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159670\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492971283\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177111\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Swingtyre\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, Swingtyre said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EChallenge:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E Safely re-enter then land a vessel with 1 stock part and an external command seat (with a kerbal riding it). If either the part or command seat are destroyed, the attempt is a failure.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo the vessel must be exactly 1 stock part \u002B 1 command seat. Both parts must land intact.\u003Cbr\u003E\nSoooo no control (would require \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E or control surfaces), no runway landing (no wheel), no parachute (command seat won\u0027t attach to chutes).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe challenge is to drop something in free fall without any mean to control it and pray that it survives... I fail to see the point or the fun in that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rath","CreatedById":138223,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-25T08:19:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps you could do it with a statically stable heatsheild and do the whole kerbals-fall-slower-than-survivable-water-impact thing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-26T20:53:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you Eva a Kerbal in midair, and it lands foot first on land, it will survive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Capt. Hunt","CreatedById":97860,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-26T20:57:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTen Meter Inflatable Heatshield.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wibou7","CreatedById":155221,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-26T21:06:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223035697\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159670\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493239998\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166583\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dundun92\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, dundun92 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you Eva a Kerbal in midair, and it lands foot first on land, it will survive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...the challenge explicitely states that the parts must land intact. EVA-ing your kerbal won\u0027t help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223035699\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159670\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493240228\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002297860\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Capt. Hunt\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, Capt. Hunt said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTen Meter Inflatable Heatshield.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s pretty much the only option. And even there there is no guarantee (you won\u0027t have any mean to control).\u003Cbr\u003E\nSo strap a heatshield on a seat, drop it from space and pray that it land safely. Rinse and repeat until it does...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-27T15:33:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223035719\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159670\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493240812\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155221\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022wibou7\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, wibou7 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...the challenge explicitely states that the parts must land intact. EVA-ing your kerbal won\u0027t help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... unless eva-ing lightens up the main ship enough where it can land intact.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cratercracker","CreatedById":171449,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-27T16:07:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223032137\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159670\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492981985\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174198\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Numerlor\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 24.04.2017 at 0:13 AM, Numerlor said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you tested this? I know it can be done with servicebay but you need to be really lucky. Nothing else comes into my mind without chutes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI presume using heatshield as some sort of a round-shaped wing,and after reentering glide down and softly ditch. (better to ditch on kerbal\u0027s head,heatshileds are fragile)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MarvinKitFox","CreatedById":99545,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-27T17:11:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, maybe I\u0027m stupid, but I fail to see the challenge?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022xZVt1ol.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/xZVt1ol.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00220whijLa.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/0whijLa.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Km5jam2.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Km5jam2.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts just a Twin Boar, command seat, and Val.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI fuel-cheated to fly it to orbit, then uncheated and landed it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould have got it to orbit the hard way, but that didn\u0027t seem needed...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CairoJack","CreatedById":169033,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-27T17:16:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223036625\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159670\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493313119\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002299545\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MarvinKitFox\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, MarvinKitFox said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmaybe I\u0027m stupid\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe are stupid !!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe forgot the Twin Boar\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wibou7","CreatedById":155221,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-27T17:54:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223036628\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159670\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493313386\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022169033\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CairoJack\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n35 minutes ago, CairoJack said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe are stupid !!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe forgot the Twin Boar\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIndeed!\u003Cbr\u003E\nFuel \u002B engine in ONE part. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/99545-marvinkitfox/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002299545\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/99545-marvinkitfox/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MarvinKitFox\u003C/a\u003E, have some reps!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-28T18:42:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EI \u003C/em\u003Edidn\u0027t forget it. That\u0027s the idea that came to me last night! I would have done that today if MarvinKitFox hadn\u0027t done it first.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-28T18:44:52Z\u0022 title=\u002204/28/2017 06:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 28, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Guest\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}